snippet.title: Webinar | Change Management Principles | Cindy Muir (Zapata) | Certificate in Executive Management
snippet.description:
Prof Cindy Muir (Zapata) delivered this webinar on Change Management Principles on June 3, 2020. She teaches in Mod 1 of Certificate in Executive Management hosted by the Stayer Center for Executive Education in the Mendoza College of Business. 

University of Notre Dame

Certificate in Executive Management is a 4-module program. You can enroll in the 4-module package or in an individual module.

Leadership Essentials (March)
Finance and Accounting for Non-Financial Managers (May)
Leading the Strategic Enterprise (Sept)
Applied Leadership Skills (Nov)

https://mendoza.nd.edu/executive-education/certificate-in-executive-management/

#NDExecEd
